I've been trying to buy a Fungi forever Finaly get the Bard says she is selling one for 25K. I say I take it. Then "its on my main but I want some cash on my bard to buy some items" "don't I know you my main is *insert some name I never heard of* (also note I was on my level 6 untaged mule that nobody should "know".) when I said no I would not give her bard part of the money she ran off and I said did you really expect me to fall for that scam, then she got all upset and said she would not deal with me...haha. She was Roleplay and guild was Deidum Battle Lords (or something close) the only other person on her guild on was some level 11 ranger. There should be something we can do about this. I'm seeing more and more Scammers try this crap.<p>--------------------</p><p>Baron Vedar <br />60 Grave Lord of the Rathe<br />Noble Blade</p>
